    "href": "https://www.xkcd.com/327/",
    "target": "_blank",
    "rel": "noreferrer"
  }), "SQL injection"), "\nis another class of attacks that are based on data being confused for code."), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "One of The Great Debates of modern times (along with \u201Ctabs vs spaces\u201D and \u201Cemacs vs vim\u201D) is embedding ", mdx("a", _extends({
